{"tid":1915051,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"錯有錯着 澳媽早前訂錯逾2000卷廁紙大派用場","createTime":"2020-03-08T02:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T04:34:04.000Z","uid":28114,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b80d03f9f1c721e095f0c41ba639b2f5e5564efa","tid":1915051,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/mZ6UGYzFF-nqZuX8Uf4zCcKA1sw=/414x232/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/RXUF6I2FEP4BZGXMSORCJUVG6A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FmZ6UGYzFF-nqZuX8Uf4zCcKA1sw%3D%2F414x232%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FRXUF6I2FEP4BZGXMSORCJUVG6A.jpg&h=27af7a63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情下澳洲多地出現民眾搶購廁紙情況，超市貨架被掃空，一個澳洲家庭竟然「洞悉先機」，上月訂購了48箱、合共逾2,000卷廁紙。這個家庭原本是訂錯數量，卻錯有錯着在全城搶紙的環境下，成功堆起廁紙牆，親友也可以鬆一口氣不用四出撲廁紙。<br />\n<br />\n住在昆士蘭的媽媽雅內茨克（Haidee Janetzki）上月在網店「Who Gives a Crap」下訂買廁紙，本來只打算買48卷，結果按錯買了48箱，即合共2,304卷廁紙。她起初未有留意信用卡賬單，結果收貨時嚇了一跳，直言「很傻、很迷茫，像個白痴一樣」。<br />\n<br />\n她的丈夫在社交網分享這則趣事，形容是「令人興奮的一天」，「我們情緒高漲，條件非常有利，我們很富有&hellip;有很多廁紙」，他更拍下妻子坐在由廁紙城牆砌成的「王座」上。<br />\n<br />\n面對澳洲各地都出現廁紙荒，雅內茨克說：「我的朋友和家人不用搶心（廁紙搶購一空），我也鬆了一口氣。」他們一家人原估計要花12年才可用完這批廁紙，眼見疫情導致廁紙難求，決定以原價在一個籌款活動上賣出部份存貨。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200307/GTQ3HQZB7BKDCNDFGL7AIJ6HKM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200307%2FGTQ3HQZB7BKDCNDFGL7AIJ6HKM%2F&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw%2F5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=769cf9f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200307%2FGTQ3HQZB7BKDCNDFGL7AIJ6HKM%2F&h=0d81f381\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200307/GTQ3HQZB7BKDCNDFGL7AIJ6HKM/</a>"},{"pid":"d20ce6051655c32b0fe9478657ed4d60837a4732","tid":1915051,"uid":18279,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:59:26.000Z","msg":"我公司都係，有個新同事訂左10箱小童口罩，本身諗住10盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61f1e89f70f813c37707f7ecd33ab65a2e44180","tid":1915051,"uid":128861,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T03:03:03.000Z","msg":"<em>眼見疫情導致廁紙難求，決定以原價在一個籌款活動上賣出部份存貨。</em><br />\n 幾好, 唔發國難財"},{"pid":"d4da4c9caeb8661197d8e1a71b10ac64263772c3","tid":1915051,"uid":264158,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c61f1e89f70f813c37707f7ecd33ab65a2e44180","tid":1915051,"uid":128861,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T03:03:03.000Z","msg":"<em>眼見疫情導致廁紙難求，決定以原價在一個籌款活動上賣出部份存貨。</em><br />\n 幾好, 唔發國難財"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T03:06:07.000Z","msg":"正想講 又搞笑 又大家有廁紙用 見到個post都開心"},{"pid":"49ae62ae7b705f9d9772c60048d07ddb76d99077","tid":1915051,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d20ce6051655c32b0fe9478657ed4d60837a4732","tid":1915051,"uid":18279,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:59:26.000Z","msg":"我公司都係，有個新同事訂左10箱小童口罩，本身諗住10盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T03:08:10.000Z","msg":"小童啱用咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5451a368f67e8f02c08ea448a70593ab38a55b45","tid":1915051,"uid":18279,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"49ae62ae7b705f9d9772c60048d07ddb76d99077","tid":1915051,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d20ce6051655c32b0fe9478657ed4d60837a4732","tid":1915051,"uid":18279,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:59:26.000Z","msg":"我公司都係，有個新同事訂左10箱小童口罩，本身諗住10盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg